    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In the armed forces of various nations, commissioned officers of the highest rank or of second or third highest rank overall, varying from one nation or organization to another.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
